**Wild Child** | Townsfolk Miscellaneous | Mini
__Basics__
The Wild Child is a young impressionable member of the townsfolk. At the first night, they must choose a role model. If their role model dies they immediately become a Wolf and member of the wolfpack.
__Details__
If the Wild Child fails to choose a role model, a random one is selected for them. They may not select themself. 
Their alignment is town for as long as their role model is alive.
